Trinity::

She smiled at him. "Nice to meet you Aerotaur.  I'm Trinity. Where 
are you taking me?" she smiled at him. Then she heard him say that he 
would take her to see her parents. Her voice rose a few 
octives,"You'll take me to see mom and dad? YIPPY!" She had a big 
grin on her face.  "WEll,  Archangle said he'd show me where mom and 
dad are.  They may be at the ship.  The one that crached near the 
other base. I hope they are ok."

(Her ship landed near the Cybertron Fire)
